      "title": "A tree fell on Hatton Colombo main road causing traffic damage",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "A huge tree has fallen down at 5.30 am today (01) in Hatton Colombo main road Kitulkala area.",
        "Due to this, there was a traffic jam on the main road and morning commuters were inconvenienced."
